```py
import logging 

logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)

x = 5
logging.info('Performing mathematical operations on x')

x = x * 2
logging.debug(f'x * 2 = {x}')

x = x + 6
logging.debug(f'x + 6 = {x}')

x = x / 4
logging.debug(f'x divided by 4 = {x}')
```

